\newlabel{fig:req1-regret}{{1}{7}{Representative Requirement 1 regret curves. Under a binding budget, UCB1 eventually depletes the budget and its regret becomes linear; under a slack budget, both learners behave like valid no-regret stochastic bandits}{figure.caption.5}{}}
