\newlabel{fig:req3-budget-dual}{{8}{12}{Requirement 3 diagnostics on \texttt {ns\_fast\_binding}. The dual variable acts as a real-time budget price, allowing the learner to react to changing competition while pacing the spend until the horizon}{figure.caption.14}{}}
